data.title: Can I return an Alamo rental car to an Enterprise location?
data.meta_description:
I have a car that I rented through Alamo rental but the nearest Alamo location is over an hour from me, not to mention traffic.

Can I return the Alamo car to the Enterprise (a parent company of Al...
data.text:
In Malaga airport, in Spain, at peak times the various car rental companies (Avis, Enterprise, EuropCar and other local ones) seem to have a share deal where they all interchange cars as needed (probably cross-charging) in order to cope with times of high demand. And they aren't even part of the same group!

So it is absolutely possible that you could do this - but you'd need to check first, otherwise they'll be very confused...
